tablefield.descr:
The accuracy of the stored geo data; 
                -2: server did not respond;
                -1: not processed yet;
                0: Unknown Location;
                1: Country level accuracy;
                2: Region;
                3: Sub-Region;
                4: Town/City/Village;
                5: Post code;
                6: Street;
                7: Intersection;
                8: Address level accuracy
